    requiresValidAllocation: 0
  - expression: 2
    speaker: 2
    text: "There\u2019s only a week left before time\u2019s up. I really need to
      start making the most out of the next few days so I can get him his gift. But
      why is the light here suddenly so\u2026 yellow?"
    useSpotlight: 0
    spotlightIndex: 0
    dependsOnBudget: 0
    requiredBudget: 0
    waitForButton: 0
    lolaStep: 0
    requiresValidAllocation: 0
  - expression: 0
    speaker: 0
    text: "*Alex looks around then proceeds to lean closer to the mirror. She pulls
      down her eyelid. In the reflection, the \u201Cwhites\u201D of her eye have
      become a distinct yellow hue*"
    useSpotlight: 0
    spotlightIndex: 0
    dependsOnBudget: 0
    requiredBudget: 0
    waitForButton: 0
    lolaStep: 0
    requiresValidAllocation: 0
  - expression: 2
    speaker: 2
    text: "My skin looks off. Multiple days of budgeting has messed up my normal
      routine and is starting to make me look like I haven\u2019t slept since my
      freshman year"
    useSpotlight: 0
    spotlightIndex: 0
    dependsOnBudget: 0
    requiredBudget: 0
